1.value:
IFF(LEFT("specifier",14) = 'Project Group ', 
    IFF(REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Project \\(') > 1 ,
		SUBSTR("specifier", REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",'Project Group') + 14, REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Project \\(') - 14),
    SUBSTR("specifier",REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",'Project Group') + 14, LENGTH("specifier") - 14)),'None')

IFF(LEFT("specifier",14) = 'Project Group ',
    SUBSTR("specifier", REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Project \\(') + 11, REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Version \\(') - REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Project \\(') - 11),
    'None')

IFF(LEFT("specifier",14) = 'Project Group ' AND REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Version \\(') > 1 AND REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' No such Version found') = 0,
    IFF(REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Job \\(') > 1,
        SUBSTR("specifier", REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Version \\(') + 11, REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Job \\(') - REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Version \\(') - 11),
    	SUBSTR("specifier", REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Version \\(') + 11, LENGTH("specifier") - REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Version \\(') - 10)),
    'None')

IFF(LEFT("specifier",14) = 'Project Group ' AND REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Job \\(') > 1 AND REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",'No such Version found') = 0,
    IFF(REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Components \\[') > 1,
        SUBSTR("specifier", REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Job \\(') + 7, REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Components \\[') - REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Job \\(') - 6),
        IFF(REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Component \\(') > 1,
            SUBSTR("specifier", REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Job \\(') + 7, REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Component \\(') - REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Job \\(') - 6),
            IFF(REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Connectors \\[') > 1,
                SUBSTR("specifier", REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Job \\(') + 7, REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Connectors \\[') - REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Job \\(') - 6),
                IFF(REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Notes \\[') > 1,
                    SUBSTR("specifier", REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Job \\(') + 7, REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Notes \\[') - REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Job \\(') - 6),
                     IFF(REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Nothing') > 1,
                         SUBSTR("specifier", REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Job \\(') + 7, REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Nothing') - REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Job \\(') - 6),
                         SUBSTR("specifier", REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Job \\(') + 7, LENGTH("specifier") - REGEXP_INSTR("specifier",' - Job \\(') - 6)))))),
    'None')
